{"data":[{"date":"15:03 14/08","title":"V\u00ec \u201ctrung \u00fay\u201d Savic, Milan s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0103n thua \u0111\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/16/milan-chi-dam-mua-milinkovicsavic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>AC Milan chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Milinkovic-Savic. H\u1ecd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1i t\u1eeb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 110 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u201chot\u201d tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Milan gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 t\u00e2n binh v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 79 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, Gonzalo Higuain l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang ti\u1ec1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Milan 18 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 36 tri\u1ec7u mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o n\u0103m sau. Ngay tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft, Higuain \u0111\u00e3 s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng \u00edt gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Milan s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 8. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1eeb Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u 1 n\u0103m k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00e2u ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Rossoneri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AC Milan chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Milinkovic-Savic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"AC Milan chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Milinkovic-Savic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/AC-Milan-chi-dam-mua-Milinkovic-Savic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Milan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 t\u00e2n binh bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Higuain</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Elliott mua l\u1ea1i Milan, h\u1ecd t\u1ecf r\u00f5 tham v\u1ecdng t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i h\u00e0o quang. M\u00f9a t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf \u0111en c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Europa League v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Milan l\u00e0 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 trung tuy\u1ebfn, AC Milan chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Milinkovic-Savic. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Lazio l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 110 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u00f3n \u201ch\u00e0ng hot\u201d tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/16/milan-chi-dam-mua-milinkovicsavic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>AC Milan chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMilan v\u1eabn d\u00f9ng c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u0169: H\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u01b0\u1ee3n Milinkovic-Savic m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 s\u1ebd mua \u0111\u1ee9t ngay m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a UEFA t\u1eebng su\u00fdt khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Milan trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. Lazio \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Milinkovic-Savic v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Milan t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng Fabio Borini nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Milan tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-xit-chelsea-ky-hop-dong-voi-ac-milan-trong-vai-gio-toi-172-194417.html\">Bom x\u1ecbt Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AC Milan trong v\u00e0i gi\u1edd t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ac-milan-nang-gia-hoi-mua-bakayoko-172-193993.html\">AC Milan n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua bom x\u1ecbt Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chi-120-trieu-euro-ac-milan-tinh-vuot-mat-mu-vu-pogba-serbia-172-193722.html\">Chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro, AC Milan t\u00ednh v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u1ee5 Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/gattuso-chang-cau-thu-nao-co-the-tu-choi-chung-toi-176-193717.html\">Gattuso: Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5480","checkdouble":"194463"},{"date":"12:15 14/08","title":"B\u00e1o Pakistan \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/bao-pakistan-dua-ra-nhan-xet-day-bat-ngo-ve-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, t\u1edd Football Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 \u01afCV cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</h2><h2>B\u00e1o Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay 14/8 trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1o Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1o Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Bao-Pakistan-noi-gi-ve-tran-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Pakistan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Pakistan \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u0110T&nbsp;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft &quot;Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao cho Pakistan trong ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c&quot; tr\u00ean t\u1edd Football Pakistan, c\u00e2y vi\u1ebft Faizan Liaquat \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao khi cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Pakistan r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n khi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ebb hay nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Faizan Liaquat c\u00f2n t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0n qu\u00e2n HLV Park Hang Seo trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t: &ldquo;H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m. Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho ASIAD khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd th\u1eafng Palestine v\u00e0 Oman, h\u00f2a Uzbekistan&rdquo;.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan-372-194453.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (Asiad 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00e2y vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Football Pakistan v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ASIAD. <o:p></o:p>Faizan Liaquat c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n Asiad 2018 v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ebb n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y b\u1edfi 14/8 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y qu\u1ed1c kh\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Pakistan. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 n\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y \u00fd ngh\u0129a t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7: &quot;L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Pakistan th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u1edf Asiad l\u00e0 n\u0103m 1974. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00f3a b\u1ecf l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n n\u00e0y v\u00e0o n\u0103m nay kh\u00f4ng? \u0110\u00e1p \u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/8 - c\u0169ng l\u00e0 Qu\u1ed1c Kh\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 n\u00e0o \u00fd ngh\u0129a h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu Pakistan t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti (Cikarang). Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ky-tich-moi-168-194454.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ky-tich-moi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ky-tich-moi-168-194454.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakist