0f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Olympic Pakistan full HD kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eadt lags tr\u00ean Internet 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 14/8.</h2><h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 VI\u1ec6T NAM VS U23 PAKISTAN</h2>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MAg4dO01ETY\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBeatVN.sport%2Fvideos%2F228008994539450%2F&amp;show_text=0&amp;width=560\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden\" scrolling=\"no\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"100%\" height=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> T\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 18, tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi U23 Pakistan di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo VTV c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1c \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Asiad 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Indonesia do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 n\u00ean NHM&nbsp;n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018 qua m\u1ea1ng Internet.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align