ss=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Video Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Video Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/video-quang-hai-mo-ti-so-cho-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede ph\u00fat 21 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i. Sau pha ban b\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Quang H\u1ea3i kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng qua ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Olympic Pakistan, m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/14/Viet-Nam-vs-Pakistan-21.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5476","checkdouble":"194478"},{"date":"14:57 14/08","title":"Real ch\u1ed1t sao Chelsea thay Marcelo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/real-chot-marcos-alonso-thay-marcelo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Alonso trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Marcelo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcelo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcelo l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Alonso  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Alonso  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Marcos-Alonso--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Marcelo t\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Marcelo t\u1edbi Juventus, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, Juventus t\u00ednh chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 30 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang <br>\r\nhy v\u1ecdng Los Blancos s\u1ebd nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ronaldo c\u0169ng \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Marcelo t\u1edbi Italia.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Marcelo t\u1edbi Italia theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nReal nh\u1eafm Alonso thay Marcelo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Alonso trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Marcelo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcos Alonso\" title=\"Marcos Alonso\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/033433-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Alonso thay Marcelo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real mua Marcos Alonso th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, b\u1edfi HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. Trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t thay v\u00ec th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEmerson Palmieri th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Marcos Alonso \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Emerson l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Thibaut Courtois</span> t\u1eeb Chelsea, h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam Marcos Alonso v\u00e0 Eden Hazard t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5475","checkdouble":"194461"},{"date":"16:20 14/08","title":"Real t\u00ednh chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t Serie A","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/real-tinh-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-pjanic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, theo Tuttosport \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Miralem Pjanic \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Juventus. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t Serie A.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/real-tinh-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-pjanic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Pjanic ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Miralem Pjanic t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 15 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Miralem Pjanic gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-mua-pjanic-172-192111.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Miralem Pjanic</span>, Man City v\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pjanic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, theo Tuttosport \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, h\u1ecd \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pjanic khang dinh chi trich Juventus la khong cong bang\" title=\"Pjanic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Juventus l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Miralem-Pjanic-thay-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pjanic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLos Blancos v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 Mateo Kovacic c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, Luka Modric c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Inter Milan. T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i bu\u1ed9c HLV Lopetegui ph\u1ea3i mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Juventus b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia, Real s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Thiago c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, Real \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea, ngo\u00e0i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 Los Blancos c\u00f2n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Marcos Alonso c\u0169ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5474","checkdouble":"194470"},{"date":"15:33 14/08","title":"Ander Herrera mang tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/ander-herrera-goi-y-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ander Herrera g\u1ee3i \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U. Giao k\u00e8o c\u0169 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 h\u1ebft hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ef1 h\u00e0o ch\u01a1i cho M.U</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnder Herrera chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Man United t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao n\u0103m 2014 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 29 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (37 tri\u1ec7u Euro) d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Louis van Gaal. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 161 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n sau 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. M\u00f9a 2016/17 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Herrera \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9 khi gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t M.U, ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9c t\u00f4n nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m c\u1ee7a David de Gea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi nay, Herrera v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Jose Mourinho. V\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 qua, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Inside United: \u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. Khi b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i cho Manchester United, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c trong m\u1ecdi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ander Herrera g\u1ee3i \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ander Herrera g\u1ee3i \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/ander-herrera-goi-y-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Herrera g\u1ee3i \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHerrera \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u1edbi M.U. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Herrera g\u1ee3i \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U. Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u FA Cup, c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n v\u00e0 Europa League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\u201d, Herrera ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng CLB. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n 160 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u00e0 trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 200 tr\u1eadn. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3i qua th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa c\u00f9ng CLB.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1ch m\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o, t\u00ecnh y\u00eau m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n. Gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Manchester v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, c\u0169ng c\u1ea5p h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i CLB.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alan-shearer-toi-se-khong-ngac-nhien-neu-pogba-toi-barca-172-194416.html\">Alan Shearer: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Pogba t\u1edbi Barca\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/thomas-muller-phat-bieu-ve-robert-lewandowski-193-194398.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real v\u00e0 M.U?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/gary-neville-noi-ve-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194351.html\">C\u1ef1u sao M.U n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-cua-minh-172-194297.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Pogba ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng khai mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-claude-puel-phat-bieu-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester-172-194263.html\">HLV Leicester: \u201cTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5473","checkdouble":"194468"},{"date":"16:04 14/08","title":"T\u1ea1i sao Raheem Sterling b\u1ecb c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/raheem-sterling-bi-phan-biet-chung-toc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Raheem Sterling b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal, Ian Wright sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sterling ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRaheem Sterling m\u1edbi ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal, m\u1edf ra chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League h\u00f4m ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 23 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho The Citizens.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Sterling \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh 6 tr\u1eadn cho \u0110T Anh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i trong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh Tam s\u01b0 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Raheem Sterling b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Raheem Sterling b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Raheem-Sterling-bi-phan-biet-chung-toc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sau nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, Sterling b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tham gia World Cup, Sterling \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfng t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn khi x\u0103m h\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t kh\u1ea9u s\u00fang l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c trong l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool c\u0169ng g\u00e2y x\u00f4n xao d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. <br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Wright</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi Sterling, c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh Ian Wright l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i: \u201cC\u00f3 bao nhi\u00eau ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch cho Sterling?\u201d, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Arsenal n\u00f3i tr\u00ean BBC Radio 5Live. \u201cNh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Sterling l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i Sterling. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n k\u00e9o Sterling xu\u1ed1ng. Khi b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c trong \u0111\u00f3. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sterling-toa-sang-tro-lai-guardiola-cau-khan-gia-han-voi-man-city-172-194465.html\">Sterling t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Guardiola c\u1ea7u kh\u1ea9n gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh-172-194405.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal 0-2 Man City: Sterling v\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-co-vai-dieu-muon-gui-den-man-city-va-sterling-172-194403.html\">Pep c\u00f3 v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Man City v\u00e0 Sterling</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/benjamin-mendy-man-tai-xuat-an-tuong-va-cau-chuyen-ve-nguoi-cha-tinh-than-pep-guardiola-389-194401.html\">Benjamin Mendy: M\u00e0n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha tinh th\u1ea7n Pep Guardiola</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5472","checkdouble":"194469"},{"date":"17:08 14/08","title":"Man City \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Arsenal nh\u1edd...Mikel Arteta","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/man-city-danh-bai-arsenal-nhomikel-arteta.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Man xanh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd t\u1eeb tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Mikel Arteta c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Arsenal 2-0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp Man City. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates, song Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arteta gi\u00fap Man City gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arteta gi\u00fap Man City gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/man-city-danh-bai-arsenal-nhomikel-arteta.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mikel Arteta t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n h\u1eefu \u00edch cho Pep</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng 42% v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 9 l\u1ea7n, 3 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, qu\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n so v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng 58%, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 17 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 8 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a Man City. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi Man xanh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRaheem Sterling v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n cho Man City. V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates, Man xanh cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HLV Emery c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1o l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd... Mikel Arteta</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Man xanh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd t\u1eeb tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Mikel Arteta c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep chuc mung Mikel Arteta voi nhung tu van chuan xac\" title=\"Pep ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Mikel Arteta v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/arteta2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Mikel Arteta v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTelegraph kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Mikel Arteta \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal, c\u1ef1u sao Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n h\u1eefu \u00edch cho nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mikel Arteta, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Mesut Ozil l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Arsenal, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng khai th\u00e1c v\u00e0o hai c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Arsenal, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0y ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Man xanh t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean, c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Sterling nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb Mendy, anh di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Petr Cech. \u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2, l\u1ea1i l\u00e0\u00a0Mendy th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 Bernardo Silva ch\u1ea1y c\u1eaft m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Cech l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5471","checkdouble":"194471"},{"date":"17:41 14/08","title":"\"MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/mu-se-khong-ban-pogba-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Wes Brown cho r\u1eb1ng Man United s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Paul Pogba chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barcelona b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Pogba \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Scott McTominay trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n hai c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn Pogba h\u1eadm h\u1ef1c mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng khai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Huyen-thoai-tin-tuong-MU-se-khong-ban-Pogba-cho-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Wes Brown tin r\u1eb1ng MU\u00a0s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Wes Brown cho r\u1eb1ng Man United s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. B\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cPogba s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man United. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ghi 1 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Pogba s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 do h\u01a1n m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Fred v\u00e0 Matic th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Fred bao s\u00e2n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u01a1 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e2ng cao nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd th\u1eddi gian tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n hay ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Premier League kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c khi gi\u00fap Man United \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1. Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ea7y tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/darmian-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu-172-194460.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-1308-them-mot-cau-thu-chinh-thuc-roi-mu-184-194411.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/08: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C r\u1eddi MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5470","checkdouble":"194472"},{"date":"17:32 14/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t sao tr\u1ebb chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/14/patrick-roberts-sap-roi-man-city-sang-girona.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Patrick Roberts s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City sang Girona. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a N\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester ra \u0111i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Roberts kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPatrick Roberts tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Fulham. Anh t\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ch\u01a1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng London t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh m\u00f9a 2014/15 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c trinh s\u00e1t vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2015, The Citizens chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ra \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1edbi, Roberts kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Trong d\u00e0n sao Man City, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 anh kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng chi\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, \u0111\u00e3 3 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, Roberts ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho N\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Patrick Roberts s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City sang Girona h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Patrick Roberts s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City sang Girona h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/patrick-roberts-sap-roi-man-city-sang-girona.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Patrick Roberts s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City sang Girona</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2015/16, Roberts \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111em cho Celtic m\u01b0\u1ee3n 2 m\u00f9a r\u01b0\u1ee1i qua. Ri\u00eang m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Girona</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Patrick Roberts s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City sang Girona. Hai c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eadt n\u00edch ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau khi h\u1ecd b\u1ed5 sung Riyad Mahrez t\u1eeb Leicester City v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t Roberts ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City nh\u1eafm mang \u0111i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0a anh t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng CLB n\u00e0o th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 Roberts tu nghi\u1ec7p h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Girona. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em c\u1ee7a Man City khi chung ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u00e0 t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n City Football Group.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n do c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 \u1ea2-R\u1eadp \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfm t\u1edbi 44.3% c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i Girona. Trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua, nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi sang CLB n\u00e0y v\u00e0 Roberts chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a The Citizens \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n sau nh\u1eefng Pablo Mar\u00ed, Erik Palmer-Brown, Mix Diskerud, Jack Harrison, Luka Ilic v\u00e0 Anthony C\u00e1ceres\u2026<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sterling-toa-sang-tro-lai-guardiola-cau-khan-gia-han-voi-man-city-172-194465.html\">Sterling t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Guardiola c\u1ea7u kh\u1ea9n gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-co-vai-dieu-muon-gui-den-man-city-va-sterling-172-194403.html\">Pep c\u00f3 v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Man City v\u00e0 Sterling</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-man-city-het-tien-mua-cau-thu-roi-172-194212.html\">Pep Guardiola: \u201cMan City h\u1ebft ti\u1ec1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i!\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-man-city-172-194132.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-khang-dinh-se-khong-mua-them-nguoi-172-194007.html\">Pep kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5469","checkdouble":"194473"},{"date":"11:47 14/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 14/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng cao nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd v\u1eeba b\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nH\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine, Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan c\u00e0ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan link xem Asiad 2018 HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan link xem Asiad 2018 HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/vietnam-pakistan-2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Pakistan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 1 trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D.\u00a0 D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c k\u1ef7 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Indonesia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu tinh th\u1ea7n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, trong 3 ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t Indonesia, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u00e2n c\u1ecf nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, do s\u00e2n c\u1ecf m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ee7a Samsung t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Java ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u2018t\u1eadp chay\u2019 tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t xi m\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (14/8).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u an \u1ee7i l\u00e0 trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o nhau gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 l\u00f2ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a NHM.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ASIAD, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m \u2018thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi kinh nghi\u1ec7m\u2019. Ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. R\u1ea5t may \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang seo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o may m\u1eafn.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5468","checkdouble":"194453"}]}